canonical:
  title: 七站途中
  author: 偰遜
  language: lzh
  text: 千山飛雪曉糢糊忽放新晴學畫圖不似江南春二月石橋流水浴雙鳧
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 七站途中
  author: 偰遜
  language: lzh
  text: 千山飛雪曉糢糊。忽放新晴學畫圖。不似江南春二月。石橋流水浴雙鳧。
korean:
  title: 칠참도중
  author: 설손
  language: kor
  text: |-
    산마다 나는 눈에 새벽이 희미하더니
    갑자기 새로운 햇빛을 놓아 마치 그림 같아라
    강남의 봄 이월달과 같지 않아서
    돌다리 흐르는 물에 오리 한 쌍이 목욕하네
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0240_010_1210&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: Seven Stages Along the Way
  author: Seol Son
  language: eng
  text: |-
    A thousand mountains wrapped in flying snow at dawn's dim light—
    Suddenly the sun breaks through, like brushstrokes on painted silk.
    Unlike the spring of the southern lands in the second month,
    A pair of ducks bathe where the stone bridge meets the flowing stream.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: The 'seven stages' in the title refers to the stages of a journey, likely a travel record or diary entry marking one station along the way
